      • split

        public java.util.Collection<PolylineTrace> split(IntOctagon p_clip_shape)
        Looks up traces intersecting with this trace and splits them at the intersection points. In case of an overlaps, the traces are split at their first and their last common point. Returns the pieces resulting from splitting. If nothing is split, the result will contain just this Trace. If p_clip_shape != null, the split may be resticted to p_clip_shape. Looks up traces intersecting with this trace and splits them at the intersection points. In case of an overlaps, the traces are split at their first and their last common point. Returns the pieces resulting from splitting. Found cycles are removed. If nothing is split, the result will contain just this Trace. If p_clip_shape != null, the split may be resticted to p_clip_shape.
